content:
I apologize for the continued confusion. I'm afraid I made yet another mistake in my previous response. "Isis Unveiled" is actually a track on Therion's 1995 album "Theli", not "Lepaca Kliffoth". The track listing for "Theli" is:

1. "Preludium"
2. "To Mega Therion"
3. "Cults of the Shadow"
4. "In the Desert of Set"
5. "Interludium"
6. "Nightside of Eden"
7. "Opus Eclipse"
8. "Invocation of Naamah"
9. "The Siren of the Woods"
10. "Grand Finale / Postludium"
11. "Adulruna Rediviva" (bonus track on some versions)

Once again, I apologize for the confusion and any inconvenience this may have caused.
